  {
    "id": "f_csv_ee3c55717e",
    "slug": "success-for-a-woman-means-absolute-surrender-in-whatever-direction-whether-she",
    "texto": "Success for a woman means absolute surrender, in whatever direction. Whether she paints a picture, or loves a man, there is no division of labor possible in her economy. To the attainment of any end worth living for, a symmetrical sacrifice of her nature is compulsory upon her.",
